{"tid":311773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遼寧廢輪入港   新渡輪被水警截停   乘客不滿斥「阻返工」","createTime":"2017-07-07T01:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T12:48:16.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c03e276872cd597b0e6226252c3809ba344db1c4","tid":311773,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T01:54:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170707/large/1499390507_3a81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170707%2Flarge%2F1499390507_3a81.jpg&h=9dbd5a1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那遼寧廢輪編隊已經進入本港水域，途經數碼港、摩星嶺，直駛往青衣。駛入香港後的航道，均是本港繁忙的水域，所以不時看到渡輪、噴射船及貨櫃船等大小船隻，在　身旁蹤橫交錯，但過程大致暢順。事實上，新渡輪亦曾發出通告，指因收到當局通知航道或受影響，故發通知提醒乘客。今早有新渡輪便一度被水警輪截停，有乘客不滿受阻遲到返工。<br />\n<br />\n讀者尹先生，今早8時05分乘渡輪由梅窩出中環，途經交椅洲對開海面，被水警小艇截停。尹說：「見到3隻戰艦響渡輪正前方駛過，冇見到遼寧廢輪，停咗10分鐘，然後仲要兜個圈駛過，船長廣播因為『水道被封，要延遲』，搞到返工遲到。」尹不滿遼寧廢輪編隊「阻街」，冇必要呢個時間入嚟，可以夜晚黑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170707/large/1499390753_f9e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170707%2Flarge%2F1499390753_f9e1.jpg&h=5116fe8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170707/large/1499391683_2046.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170707%2Flarge%2F1499391683_2046.jpg&h=aae11dee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c6e510cf03dfc919014843cbd13755c55799b51","tid":311773,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T01:55:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>尹不滿遼寧廢輪編隊「阻街」，冇必要呢個時間入嚟，可以夜晚黑。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n夜晚黑入港, 視野唔好, <br />\n隻遼寧廢輪怕被撞沉啦<br />\n<br />\n斷龍骨架佢"},{"pid":"bd766915b74fb060594676e6eaced383aa38a085","tid":311773,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T01:57:07.000Z","msg":"貨輪真係要小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af10256dc7de17351b86c578491cdcd9389846de","tid":311773,"uid":75445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T02:00:36.000Z","msg":"阻撚住哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095d4b977176f9716afaad8d507d9db509d7e697","tid":311773,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T02:04:06.000Z","msg":"1. 夜晚入港, 視野唔好, 支那雷達垃圾, 觸礁點算<br />\n2. 唔停隻渡輪, 一個唔該支那第一隻艦就比隻渡輪撞沉左gg, 咁點算？開戰？"},{"pid":"c6051663c6e015cd388c74ac6eee8ff7147d8e50","tid":311773,"uid":42820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T02:04:29.000Z","msg":"支那之前見原來貨輪都可以撞爛美帝戰艦<br />\n而家應該連舢舨都驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5aed7f68aeac44f045e31d33bc24cbbec5cae3e","tid":311773,"uid":103325,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T02:07:24.000Z","msg":"原來新渡輪係遼撚剋星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"460c50a4d33cb64ce89b890115ce1a68251a0e58","tid":311773,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T02:10:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來新渡輪係遼撚剋星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n遼寧廢輪改名做「熊貓號」啦<br />\n<br />\n受保護輪船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a633242f2b8bf6b90ad78131814fbf634948956a","tid":311773,"uid":46420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T02:16:59.000Z","msg":"頭先坐船見到有隻滅火輪噴哂水歡迎隻航母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實,係咪驚佢會自爆,所以噴定水準備呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9e2290536a9