73,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T03:03:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那之前見原來貨輪都可以撞爛美帝戰艦<br />\n而家應該連舢舨都驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n美國隻驅逐艦相比之下真係神盾級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c420d85d8102d869e95fc0ecea5bb0586d2b763d","tid":311773,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T03:05:00.000Z","msg":"本身都無乜野, <br />\n屌, 但係又要拎出黎展覽打晒飛機, 做乜9"},{"pid":"cf1a19e1e5bd6af270c422f7a13d6f927c99875a","tid":311773,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T03:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170707/large/1499390753_f9e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170707%2Flarge%2F1499390753_f9e1.jpg&h=5116fe8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170707/large/1499391683_2046.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170707%2Flarge%2F1499391683_2046.jpg&h=aae11dee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貨柜船"},{"pid":"5cf8bb2d25193be5ae54ff64b1d4df27dc15719c","tid":311773,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T04:18:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06d8bb5c7e2ec80d2afc0f1c8390aaf4b9e5e393","tid":311773,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T04:26:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">艦隊指揮唔熟港水域：廢輪停泊「維多尼亞灣」</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170707/56924847\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170707%2F56924847&d=eufLZs2OTZj7nUe3CMdYibIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=dfe1e769\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170707%2F56924847&h=f2b6ebcb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170707/56924847</a><br />\n<br />\n丁毅指，今次來港參加匪軍佔港20年活動，3艘屬輪會停泊在昂船洲軍營，遼寧廢輪就會停泊維港，但他就錯將維多利亞港讀成「維多利亞灣」。<br />\n<br />\n他稱船隊上月在青島啟航進行訓練，結果令人滿意。今次來港首次面向殖民公眾，料有5萬人來參觀，官兵侵港期間亦會參與社區活動；又指佔港以來本港發生翻天覆地的改變。"}]}